egypt author to buy pl 480 wheat flour-usda egypt ha been author to purchas about 125,000 tonn of u.s. wheat flour under an exist pl 480 agreement , the u.s. agricultur depart said . it may buy the wheat flour , valu at 23.0 mln dlr between april 8 and august 31 , 1987 and ship it by septemb 30 , the depart said .